<h1 align="center">
  My web portfolio on gatsby
</h1>

Lately I have set new challenges, learn new technologies and above all practice my English language.
For this and more reasons I decided to change my web portfolio to gatsby, without modifying my styles, in order to practice this technology and add one more skill to my resume.

I hope you enjoy..

## 🚀 Quick start

1.  **Clone or download the file.**

   You can type the command:

    ```
     git clone https://github.com/makiavellipac/portfolio-gatsby.git
    ```

2.  **Start developing.**

    Navigate into your new site’s directory and start it up.

    ```shell
    cd portfolio-gatsby/
    gatsby develop
    ```
